-- MOVES-Societe Generale Corporate & Investment banking hires Nick Gionfriddo 
-- 
-- Thu Dec 11, 2014 02:40PM EST
-- None



Dec 11 (Reuters) - Societe Generale Corporate & Investment Banking appointed Nick Gionfriddo as Head of OTC Clearing Sales, North America, within its Newedge services business.

Gionfriddo joins Societe Generale from SME Group, where he was a senior director. He has more than 11 years of derivatives clearing experience in operations, solutions and marketing within global financial services organizations.